summary: I am a proactive geologist and environmental scientist with specialist and research experiences in Reservoir Characterization, Basin Analysis and Environmental Systems Analysis units accrued within Africa, Asia and Europe. My experience spans between the oil and gas sector and environmental sector. My areas of interests are Geology, Environmental Science and Environmental Engineering Management.
